8T16:21:32.75","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"offspec claim still outstanding but risk reduced to low, therefore reduced our reservation in this to $113k USD"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-01-09T11:48:06.003","modifiedByFull":"Ervasti, Josh","remark":"added 50% reservation for off spec cargo claim (bad cleaning clause with owners so not sure we can pass on)"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-12-08T16:01:35.393","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"Difference: Originally the vessel was to load Jet, Gasoline, and Diesel, however the diesel was loaded and immediately found to be off spec. After having all P\u0026I clubs join the vessel for sampling, all results pointed to a shore side issue resulting from sediment in the lines. Diesel was discharged back to shore per Chevron\u0027s orders and vessel sailed with about 140k BBLs of product onboard. Freight increased due to two additional ECCA discharge ports. With extended time in the load port, we had almost 11 days of demurrage at $35k/day. Bunkers increased due to more days in load port and a speed up enroute to the discharge port. We billed Chevron $12k of the additional bunkers consumed shifting to the anchorage while waiting for instructions and also for discharging the off spec cargo back to shore. Once the vessel arrived to the disport, all operations went smoothly."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-12-04T18:23:09.873","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Puerto Barrios costs less than est."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-11-20T18:00:11.26","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Santo Tomas port costs less than est."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-11-13T15:41:06.24","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Additional bunkers consumed due to offspec cargo discharge and shifting included to be billed to charterers"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-11-01T14:39:34.34","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Port costs in Puerto Cortes 10k lower than expected."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-10-25T19:04:20.147","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Demurrage had somehow been taken out. Included it now."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-10-09T18:56:11.06","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Issue with the cargo spec. Vessel delayed in Pascagoula"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-10-03T14:45:20.58","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Port costs included for Discharge ports.And Max port costs fixed from generation."},{"modifiedDate":"2023-10-02T20:09:47.89","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"extended time in Pascagoula"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-10-02T12:52:51.66","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Two additional ports added in ECCA"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-10-02T12:46:48.427","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Max Port Expenses: 35k Honduras, 25k Guatemala"}],"offhireList":[],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}